# ======================================================================
# == Definitive .gitattributes for The Phoenix Protocol               ==
# ======================================================================
#
# Enforce consistent line endings for all text files.
# This prevents cross-platform issues and suppresses CRLF/LF warnings.
# On checkout, text files will be converted to the OS's native line ending.
# On commit, they will be normalized to LF in the repository.

* text=auto eol=lf